	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-06-19T03:33:49">African Potash Limited is a United Kingdom-based potash exploration company. The Company is engaged in the acquisition and development of potash assets. The Company focuses on potash-related investments in sub-Saharan Africa. The Company's projects include Lac Dinga Project, in which the Company holds around 70% interest. The Lac Dinga Project is located in the south-west of the Republic of Congo, and covers approximately 702 square kilometers and hosts a range of deposits. African Potash (Mauritius) Limited is a subsidiary of the Company.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2016-01-11T13:39:04">BRIEF: For the fiscal year ended 30 June 2015, African Potash Ltd revenues was not reported. Net loss increased from $1M to $7.2M. Higher net loss reflects Operating expenses increase of 21% to $1.2M (expense), Finance (expense) / income decrease from $1K (income) to $134K (expense). Basic Earnings per Share excluding Extraordinary Items totaled to -$0.02.</Text>
